properties.name: Ethereal Planes
properties.description:
Join us as we visit at least two airports that are no more, one helipad that remains, and an extended portion of the "other" LA River bike path (which may or may not exist, depending on one's perspective on the whole thing). Ethereal!

At times, you may even feel like you are flying, because there are some hills this week, yes indeed. And they love you, these hills, as only hills can. What they take out of your legs, they give back to your eyes, and then some!

Also: horses, mansions, tunnels, trains, and more!
